Creating Line and Stacked Column Chart for Each Month 13

Creating Line and Stacked Column Chart for Violation Per Month by Month, Gender, YOY and Out of State Violation

Steps

Violation Per Month in each Month, Gender, YOY and Out of State Violation

  1.        Open Visualization Pane
  2.        Select   Line and Stacked Column Chart 
  3.        Drag the visual on to the dashboard
  4.        Drag Month field from Date table to Shared Axis, Gender Field to Column series, Violation Per Month Measure to Column Values, YOY and %Out of State Measure to Line values 

                                               



Download the formatting for the above visual  by clicking the red icon
